(44, 2, 27, 66, 20, 13, 13, 'soul in hell', 'Connection of Death and Judgment', 'This connection highlights the theme of death and the afterlife. Acts 2:27 speaks of not leaving the soul in hell, while Revelation 20:13 discusses hell delivering up the dead for judgment.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
