(44, 2, 28, 20, 2, 19, 19, 'ways of life', 'Paths of Life Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of life and joy. Acts 2:28 speaks of the ''ways of life'' leading to joy, while Proverbs 2:19 warns that those who do not follow the right paths do not return, emphasizing the importance of choosing the correct way.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
